{"color":"DEFAULT","isTrashed":false,"isPinned":false,"isArchived":false,"textContent":"Pull up machine - 90 lbs 10, 80 lbs 10, 10...2 NROM\nReverse pec deck fly - 70 lbs 12, 80 lbs 10, 80lbs>70lbs 9>3\nLat pulldown - 125 lbs 10, 125 lbs 12, 187lbs>125 lbs 5F>4F, 87 lbs 5 fast, 5 slow, 1 hold 5 sec\nChest-supported rows - 87 lbs 12, 12, 100 lbs 11F\nDb shoulder shrugs / Lat raise - 30 lbs/15 lbs 15/12, 35lbs/15lbs 15/12, 15*/12\nBarbell row - big bar + 2x(10lbs+5lbs) 10, 10**, 10**\nPreacher curl - 20 lbs 10, 50lbs>40lbs 4...1***>4, 40 lbs>20 lbs 6F>4\nFacepull - 77 lbs 10, 10, 88 lbs>77 lbs 7>3\nForearm curl / Reverse forearm curl - 15 lbs/10 lbs 15/15, 15/12, 15/12\nBicep curl - 20 lbs>15 lbs 5~5...2~2>4~4, 4~4F...1~1>3~3, 20lbs>15lbs>10lbs 4~4>2~2>7~5...0~2\nFarmer's walk - rack>water jug>counter>water jug>counter>rack 1, 1\n\nNotes:\n* - forearm nangangawit\n** - applied the technique where you hold the bar for 1 sec before descent \n*** - accidentally put the caret on the wrong weight \n\nWeight: 79.3 kg\nPlace: Tohlda Gym\n\n","title":"January 2, 2026","userEditedTimestampUsec":1767358539771000,"createdTimestampUsec":1767351211713000,"textContentHtml":"<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Pull up machine - 90 lbs 10, 80 lbs 10, 10...2 NROM<\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Reverse pec deck fly - 70 lbs 12, 80 lbs 10, 80lbs&gt;70lbs 9&gt;3<\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;marg